  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "F&B Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and professional appearance</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Strong attention to detail</li>\n  <li>Basic math skills for handling payments</li>\n  <li>Ability to stand for extended periods</li>\n  <li>Team player with a willingness to learn</li>\n  <li>Previous experience in hospitality is a plus</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of food safety regulations is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Reliable and punctual</li>\n  <li>Customer-focused mindset</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet and welcome guests upon arrival</li>\n  <li>Take accurate food and beverage orders</li>\n  <li>Serve food and drinks promptly and professionally</li>\n  <li>Maintain the cleanliness of dining and service areas</li>\n  <li>Handle guest inquiries and resolve complaints</li>\n  <li>Follow health, safety, and hygiene standards</li>\n  <li>Restock supplies and assist with inventory</li>\n  <li>Support team members as needed</li>\n  <li>Adhere to company policies and procedures</li>\n  <li>Operate cash registers, take payments, and give receipts.</li>\n  <li>Ensure high standards of customer service are maintained.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates, kindly submit your detailed resume indicating your Last drawn salary, expected salary, and Notice period.</p>",
